=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好乖乖又親人，又唔會亂吠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"巴打有養金毛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:42:04.000Z","msg":"無，但真係好鐘意佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好可愛"},{"pid":"76d1794214ab12072b1dad9ab713a46470a04b52","tid":981950,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed488b7f272333adb146338cdc3bb6e53a38a421","tid":981950,"uid":124140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意金毛但覺得佢夏天好慘<br />\n所以如果有機會養我會諗拉布拉多<br />\n有無狗主分享下拉布拉多易唔易養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"唔難既 毛易打理過金毛 不過都係會甩到周圍係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我果隻好為食 好痴人 又怕熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細過果陣多數會好活躍 要用多d時間同佢地出去玩 唔係會成日係屋企搞搞陣 亂咬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414cd7ddfa7f875977b7b08413237c06d73d8fea","tid":981950,"uid":178317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:49:42.000Z","msg":"養狗好大責任,記住一定要諗清楚<br />\n到佢晚年你會用好多好多時間精神同金錢係佢身上<br />\n真係準備好既先好養"},{"pid":"c4d3bea681c4fc5579faa7e13b9453d833bbfac3","tid":981950,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"細狗就約瑟 貴婦"},{"pid":"b58e37dd8316a4b62b6f9ab3f9108cb902aa3645","tid":981950,"uid":200898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T18:04:43.000Z","msg":"厹"},{"pid":"ae1ec98ea4e063ee78ba7cf82a4bc7ec6df0216e","tid":981950,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手領養可以好/唔好<br />\n好：上手教得好咪易接手，打齊針絕哂育<br />\n唔好：唔係養大，唔知狗習性/底線，等等<br />\n<br />\n唔係屋企大就有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題會唔會帶佢出街，同其他狗玩<br />\n仲有幾多時間花係佢身上陪佢<br />\n<br />\n始終覺得由狗bb開始養最好<br />\n因為有好多野係細狗開始陪養同建立關係<br />\n但正常人返工佢實會屋企倒亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非有個學生哥可以長期陪住佢<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂，養左就唔好棄養<br />\n有咩google都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6695d5180f92960e0f771d873aecce1c183d046e","tid":981950,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fbe9980841e9310adfc0e5587ff158918965857","tid":981950,"uid":183219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"如果領養 邊到最好？愛協？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"愛協大部份都係唐狗黎<br />\n樓上講得岩, 其實咩品種都唔緊要, 岩個陣無論咩品種外觀, 你都會接受哂<br />\n如果未有心水品種, 不如多D去愛協或者出面有D領養日接觸多D狗先, 到時你就知自己想要咩"},{"pid":"bc76abacc20fe06abdff41a066217ce4df6675d0","tid":981950,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"其實唐狗都好得意，而且忠心，性格又好，唔似某d名種狗成個港女咁臭串。唐狗又少病痛遺傳病，真心非常適合新手養"},{"pid":"b072bb67e5eb96eab9db2e859ae4eb9a0ca51699","tid":981950,"uid":222071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"In 哥基 we trust"},{"pid":"4b3d5575e48b5f50709fb8328e7a4bdf8e0c5eec","tid":981950,"uid":222071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"哥基好聰明，又可愛"},{"pid":"ddd883fc2a5d6cde4325ebd0d23dde67c891d3ef","tid":981950,"uid":226612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"冇狗係適合新手 全部都要曬好多時間精力精神 每日要帶出街 梳毛 洗耳 陪玩 睇醫生每次至少過500 每月保健100 任何狗都係 有啲品種會有遺傳基因問題 樓主咁問我真係好懷疑樓主係咪真心鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78844aa8d701259a12253d850b7feb61abb2fd72","tid":981950,"uid":226612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"念清楚真係有心養就領養啦"},{"pid":"c4acf7c187094cf361b7cbea629fd84678eba70b","tid":981950,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:40:45.000Z","msg":"pug<img src=\"/